stream
q 0.92 g 50 710 512 50 re f Q
BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 284.4 740 Td (Chapter 1) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 16 Tf 152.4 720 Td (YOUR BODY IS CHANGING \(AND THAT'S GOOD!\)) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Your body is doing something incredible right now. It is growing from a girl's) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (body into a woman's body, and that process is called puberty. It usually starts) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (between ages 8 and 13, though every girl's timeline is different. There is no) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td ('right' age to start.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Puberty happens because your brain sends chemical signals called hormones) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (through your body. These hormones, especially estrogen, tell your body it is) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (time to grow and change. Think of hormones as text messages from your brain to) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (your body parts saying 'hey, time to level up!') Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (You might notice changes happening all at once, or they might come gradually) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (over several years. Some girls develop earlier than their friends, some later.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (Both are completely normal. Your body has its own schedule and it knows exactly) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (what it is doing.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (Changes you might notice: growing taller quickly, body shape changing \(hips) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (getting wider\), skin becoming oilier, sweating more, new hair growing in) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (different places, breasts beginning to develop, and eventually getting your) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 419 Td (period. All of these are signs that your amazing body is working perfectly.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (It is totally normal to have mixed feelings about these changes. You might feel) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (excited one day and nervous the next. You might wish your body would hurry up or) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 362 Td (slow down. Whatever you feel is valid. This book is here to help you understand) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 347 Td (every change and feel confident through all of them.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
