BT 0.2 g /F2 11 Tf 72 675 Td (Q: Is this normal?) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 10 Tf 82 659 Td (A:  Yes! Almost certainly. Every girl goes through puberty differently, and) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 10 Tf 82 645 Td (   there is a wide range of normal. If you are ever truly concerned, ask) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 10 Tf 82 631 Td (   your doctor.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 11 Tf 72 602 Td (Q: When will it happen to me?) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 10 Tf 82 586 Td (A:  Your body has its own timeline. Comparing yourself to friends is not) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 10 Tf 82 572 Td (   helpful because everyone develops at their own pace. Trust your body.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 11 Tf 72 543 Td (Q: What if mine is different from my friends?) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 10 Tf 82 527 Td (A:  Bodies are wonderfully diverse. Different is not wrong. Different is) Tj ET
BT 0.3 g /F4 10 Tf 82 513 Td (   just different. Celebrate what makes your body unique.) Tj ET
