q 0.92 g 50 710 512 50 re f Q
BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 284.4 740 Td (Chapter 2) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 16 Tf 236.88 720 Td (BREAST DEVELOPMENT) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (One of the first visible signs of puberty for most girls is breast development.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (It usually begins with small, tender bumps behind the nipples called breast) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (buds. This can start as early as age 8 or as late as 13. One side often starts) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (before the other, and that is completely normal!) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Breast development happens in stages over several years. First come the breast) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (buds, then the area around the nipple \(areola\) gets larger and darker, then the) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (breasts grow fuller. The whole process can take 3 to 5 years. There is no way to) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (speed it up or slow it down.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (Every woman's breasts are different in size, shape, and color. There is no) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td ('ideal' size. Small breasts, large breasts, and everything in between are all) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (normal and healthy. Your breast size is determined mostly by genetics, the same) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (way your eye color is.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (You might want a bra when breasts start developing, either for comfort or) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (confidence. Sports bras and training bras are great first options. Ask a mom,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (aunt, or trusted woman to help you find one that fits comfortably. There is no) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 419 Td (rule about when you 'should' start wearing one.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (Important: breast tenderness before your period is normal. If you ever notice) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (unusual pain, lumps, or discharge, it is okay to tell a parent or doctor. Taking) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 362 Td (care of your body is not embarrassing, it is smart.) Tj ET

endstream
