BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 284.4 740 Td (Chapter 3) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 16 Tf 271.44 720 Td (BODY HAIR) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (During puberty, hair starts growing in new places. Usually, it appears under) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (your arms and in your pubic area first, then on your legs. This is completely) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (natural and happens to every woman on earth. The hair might be thin and light at) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (first, then become thicker and darker over time.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (There is no medical reason to remove body hair. It is there for protection and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (warmth. Whether you choose to shave, wax, or leave your body hair natural is) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (entirely your personal choice. There is no wrong answer. Different cultures have) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (different views on body hair.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (If you decide to try shaving, here are some tips: use a clean razor, always use) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (shaving cream or soap, shave in the direction the hair grows at first, and never) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (share razors. Ask a trusted adult to show you the first time. Small cuts are) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (normal at first.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (Pubic hair is nothing to be embarrassed about. It serves an important purpose by) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (protecting sensitive skin. It is a sign that your body is maturing normally. You) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (never need to feel ashamed of it or compare yourself to what you see in media.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 407 Td (Fun fact: the texture, color, and amount of body hair varies enormously between) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (girls and is determined by genetics. Girls from different ethnic backgrounds may) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (have more or less hair. All variations are normal and healthy.) Tj ET

endstream
