BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Those same hormones that cause puberty can also cause your skin to produce more) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (oil. This extra oil can clog pores and cause pimples, blackheads, and breakouts.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (Almost every teenager gets acne to some degree. It does not mean you are dirty) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (or doing something wrong.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Basic skincare for puberty: wash your face twice daily with a gentle cleanser) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (\(not soap\), do not scrub hard or pop pimples \(this makes them worse and can) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (cause scars\), use oil-free moisturizer, and change your pillowcase often. These) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (simple steps help a lot.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (If your acne is severe or very painful, it is okay to see a dermatologist. They) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (have treatments that can help. Acne is a medical condition, not a character) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (flaw. Many adults still deal with it too. You should never feel embarrassed) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (about seeking help.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (What does NOT cause acne: eating chocolate, being dirty, or touching your face) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (occasionally. What CAN make it worse: stress, not washing makeup off before bed,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (and hormonal changes around your period.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 407 Td (Remember that social media photos use filters and editing. Nobody's skin is) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (perfect all the time. Even the girls who look flawless in photos have breakouts.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (Acne is temporary and does not define you or your beauty.) Tj ET

endstream
