BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (During puberty, you might grow several inches in just one year! This rapid) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (growth is called a growth spurt. Girls typically have their biggest growth spurt) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (about 1-2 years before getting their first period. You might wake up one morning) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (and your pants are suddenly too short.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Growth spurts can cause 'growing pains,' which are aches in your legs,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (especially at night. They are not actually caused by growing itself but by) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (muscle fatigue from your rapidly growing bones. Stretching, warm baths, and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (gentle massage can help with discomfort.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (Your body might feel awkward during growth spurts. Your feet might grow before) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (the rest of you, or your legs might seem disproportionally long. You might feel) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (clumsy or trip over things more. This is temporary! Your body is adjusting to) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (its new proportions.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (Girls typically reach their full adult height about 2 years after their first) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (period begins. Most girls are close to their adult height by age 14 or 15,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (though some continue growing until 16 or 17. Your final height is mostly) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 419 Td (determined by genetics.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (During growth spurts, your body needs extra nutrition and rest. Eating well) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (\(especially calcium for bones and protein for muscles\) and getting enough sleep) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 362 Td (\(9-11 hours for teens\) helps your body grow strong and healthy.) Tj ET

