BT 0.5 g /F1 10 Tf 284.4 740 Td (Chapter 6) Tj ET
BT 0.1 g /F2 16 Tf 213.84 720 Td (PERIODS EXPLAINED SIMPLY) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Getting your period \(also called menstruation\) is a completely natural process) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (that happens to every woman. Here is what is actually happening: each month,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (your uterus builds up a soft lining of tissue and blood in case a fertilized egg) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (needs a cozy place to grow. If there is no pregnancy, the lining sheds. That) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 620 Td (shedding is your period.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (Most girls get their first period between ages 10 and 15. There is no way to) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (predict exactly when yours will come, but it usually arrives about 2 years after) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (breast development begins. You might notice a white or yellowish discharge in) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 548 Td (your underwear for several months before your first period.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (A typical period lasts 3 to 7 days. The blood might be bright red, dark brown,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (or even slightly pink. It might come out steadily or in small gushes. All of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (these are normal. You will probably use 3 to 6 pads or tampons per day,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 476 Td (depending on your flow.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (Your first few periods might be irregular, coming randomly for the first year or) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (two. This is normal as your body figures out its cycle. Eventually, most women) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 419 Td (develop a cycle between 21 and 35 days \(measured from the first day of one) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 404 Td (period to the first day of the next\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (Important: getting your period does not mean anything is wrong with you. It is a) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 362 Td (sign that your body is healthy and working exactly as designed. It is not gross,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 347 Td (shameful, or dirty. It is biology, and it is nothing to be embarrassed about.) Tj ET

endstream
