BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Pads are the most popular choice for beginners. They stick to the inside of your) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (underwear and absorb blood. They come in different sizes and thicknesses for) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (light, medium, and heavy flow. Change them every 3-4 hours. Many girls start) Tj ET
