BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (walking or stretching, over-the-counter pain relief \(ask a parent first\),) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (drinking warm tea, taking a warm bath, or lying in a comfortable position with) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (your knees drawn up.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (PMS stands for Premenstrual Syndrome. It refers to symptoms that happen in the) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (week before your period: mood swings, bloating, headaches, food cravings,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (tiredness, breast tenderness, and feeling emotional. Not every girl gets PMS,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (and symptoms vary widely.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (PMS happens because hormone levels change before your period. Eating well,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (exercising regularly, getting enough sleep, and reducing stress can all help) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (manage PMS symptoms. If PMS severely affects your life, a doctor can help.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 407 Td (It is important to track your period on a calendar or app so you can predict) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (when PMS and cramps might happen. Knowing when to expect them helps you prepare) Tj ET
