BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (During puberty, your sweat glands become more active, especially under your arms) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (and in your genital area. This sweat mixes with bacteria on your skin and can) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (cause body odor. It is nothing to be ashamed of; it happens to everyone. Good) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (hygiene manages it easily.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Daily hygiene during puberty: shower or bathe daily, use deodorant or) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (antiperspirant under your arms, wear clean underwear and clothes each day, wash) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (your face morning and night, and keep your hair clean. These simple habits keep) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (you feeling fresh and confident.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (Your vaginal area cleans itself naturally. You only need to wash the outside) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (with warm water. Never use scented soaps, sprays, or douches inside or around) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (your vagina. They can disrupt your natural pH balance and cause infections.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (Simple warm water is best.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (Some vaginal discharge is normal and healthy. It is your body's way of keeping) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (itself clean. Healthy discharge is clear or slightly white and does not have a) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (strong smell. If discharge is green, gray, smells bad, or causes itching, tell a) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 419 Td (parent or doctor.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (Sweating more during sports or hot weather is normal. Keep spare deodorant in) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (your locker or bag. Wearing breathable fabrics like cotton helps reduce sweat.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 362 Td (Remember: everybody sweats. It is how your body cools itself down.) Tj ET

endstream
