BT 0.1 g /F2 16 Tf 221.52 720 Td (EMOTIONS ROLLERCOASTER) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (During puberty, hormones do not just change your body. They also affect your) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (brain and emotions. You might feel happy one minute and want to cry the next.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (You might get angry at things that never bothered you before. You might feel) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (overwhelmed, sensitive, or moody. This is all normal.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Your brain is literally rewiring itself during puberty. The emotional part of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (your brain is developing faster than the rational part, which is why feelings) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (can feel so HUGE and intense right now. This is not a flaw in your design. It is) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (a feature of growing up.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (What helps with emotional ups and downs: getting enough sleep \(seriously, this) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (is huge\), regular exercise, talking to someone you trust, writing in a journal,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (creative expression \(art, music, dance\), and being patient with yourself. You) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (are not crazy. You are growing.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (It is okay to cry. It is okay to need alone time. It is okay to not know why you) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (feel a certain way. It is okay to ask for help. Your feelings are VALID even) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (when they do not make logical sense. Feelings do not need to be logical to be) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 419 Td (real.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (If you feel persistently sad, anxious, or hopeless for more than two weeks,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (please tell a trusted adult. Depression and anxiety can start during puberty and) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 362 Td (are treatable medical conditions, not weaknesses. Getting help is brave.) Tj ET

endstream
