BT 0.1 g /F2 16 Tf 229.2 720 Td (CRUSHES AND FEELINGS) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (During puberty, you might start feeling attracted to other people in new ways.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (You might develop crushes on classmates, celebrities, or even teachers. These) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (feelings are a normal part of growing up. Some girls develop crushes early, some) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (later, and some not for a long time. All timelines are normal.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Crushes can feel overwhelming. Your heart races, you cannot stop thinking about) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (them, you might feel nervous or giddy around them. These physical reactions are) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (caused by chemicals in your brain, especially dopamine \(the feel-good chemical\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (It is literally like a temporary brain storm.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (Having crushes does not mean you need to act on them right now. There is no rush) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (to date, kiss, or have a boyfriend or girlfriend. You are allowed to just FEEL) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (things without taking action. Enjoying the butterflies without pressure is) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (perfectly fine.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (Some girls develop crushes on boys, some on girls, and some on both. All of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (these feelings are normal and valid. Your attractions might change over time as) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (you learn more about yourself. There is no timeline for figuring this out.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 407 Td (The most important thing about crushes and romantic feelings: you never owe) Tj ET
