BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Your body is changing into shapes you might not be used to. Hips widening,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (breasts growing, fat redistributing. Media shows you one 'ideal' body type, but) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (the truth is that healthy bodies come in endless varieties. Your value has) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (nothing to do with your shape or size.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (The images you see in magazines, Instagram, and TV are not reality. They are) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (filtered, edited, posed, and often surgically enhanced. Comparing your real,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (living, beautiful body to manufactured images will always make you feel) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (inadequate because you are comparing reality to fantasy.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (Instead of focusing on how your body LOOKS, try focusing on what it CAN DO. Can) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (it run? Dance? Hug? Create? Think? Your body is a miracle of engineering that) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (keeps you alive and allows you to experience the world. That is what matters) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 491 Td (most.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (If you find yourself constantly criticizing your body, try talking to yourself) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (the way you would talk to your best friend. Would you tell her she is ugly or) Tj ET
