BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Your body is growing rapidly during puberty and needs quality fuel. This is not) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (about dieting or restriction. It is about giving your body what it needs to grow) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (strong, develop properly, and have energy for all the amazing things you want to) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (do.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (Key nutrients during puberty: calcium for growing bones \(dairy, leafy greens,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (fortified foods\), iron especially once periods start \(red meat, spinach, beans\),) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (protein for growing muscles \(chicken, fish, beans, nuts\), and healthy fats for) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (brain development \(avocado, nuts, olive oil\).) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (Eating regularly is important. Skipping meals slows your metabolism and deprives) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (your growing body of needed fuel. Aim for three meals and two snacks daily. Eat) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (when you are hungry and stop when you are full. Your body knows what it needs.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 479 Td (Dieting during puberty can be harmful because your body needs calories to grow) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (and develop properly. If someone suggests you need to lose weight, talk to your) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (doctor first. Growing bodies need MORE nutrition, not less. Health is about) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 434 Td (nourishment, not restriction.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 407 Td (Water is essential during puberty. Aim for 6-8 glasses daily, more when active.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (Dehydration can worsen headaches, fatigue, and skin problems. Keep a water) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 377 Td (bottle with you and sip throughout the day. Your body and skin will thank you.) Tj ET

endstream
