BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (It can feel awkward to talk to parents or other adults about puberty, periods,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 665 Td (or body changes. But having a trusted adult you can ask questions is important.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 650 Td (They went through the same things and can help you navigate this time with less) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 635 Td (confusion and anxiety.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 608 Td (If talking to a parent feels too awkward, consider: an older sister, aunt,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 593 Td (grandmother, school nurse, coach, or family friend. It helps to start with 'I) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 578 Td (have a question about something I read' or 'Can I ask you about something) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 563 Td (private?' These openings make the conversation easier.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 536 Td (Adults want to help you but might not know you need them unless you ask. They) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 521 Td (might be waiting for you to bring it up because they do not want to embarrass) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 506 Td (you. Someone has to go first, and it is okay if that person is you.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 479 Td (You deserve accurate information about your body. If an adult cannot answer your) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (question or seems uncomfortable, it is okay to ask a different adult or look for) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 449 Td (age-appropriate books and websites. Knowledge about your own body is your right.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 422 Td (Remember: there is no question too embarrassing or too small. Every woman alive) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 407 Td (has gone through puberty. They understand. And helping you through it is one of) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 11 Tf 72 392 Td (the most important things an adult can do.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
